    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Alternate 1: Alternate reference voltage supplied via CH0 of a converter group"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Two plausibility checks 1. 2V5 ADC reference plausibility check with 3V3 reference 2. 3V3 ADC reference plausibility check with 2V5 reference"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "If the measured ADC signal is out of range, System reset shall be initiated via Safe state Handler"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The range of upper and lower limit for both plausibility checks has to be mentioned in the HSI"
    },
    {
